trans-unit.source: Provides data for the events in the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart"></xref> control that change the position of the annotation.
trans-unit.target: Tillhandahåller data för händelser i den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart"> </xref> kontroll som ändra placeringen av anteckningen.

trans-unit.source: The AnnotationPositionChangingEventArgs class is used for the two annotation-positioning events, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanging> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanged>, in the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> control.
trans-unit.target: Klassen AnnotationPositionChangingEventArgs används för de två händelserna placeringen av anteckningen <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanging>och <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanged>i den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>kontroll.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanged> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanging>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationPositionChangingEventArgs.Annotation%2A> property gets the annotation object that is being positioned.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationPositionChangingEventArgs.Annotation%2A>egenskapen hämtar objektet anteckning som som placerats.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationPositionChangingEventArgs.Annotation%2A>

trans-unit.source: This class also contains properties that retrieve the new location, width, height and anchor location of the annotation that is repositioned.
trans-unit.target: Den här klassen innehåller också egenskaper som hämtar ny plats, bredd, höjd och fästpunkt plats för anteckning som flyttas.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.AnnotationPositionChangingEventArgs> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.AnnotationPositionChangingEventArgs>klassen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.AnnotationPositionChangingEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Annotation"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Annotation"> </xref> objekt.

trans-unit.source: The Annotation property allows the developer to set <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Annotation> properties during the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanging> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanged> events of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> control.
trans-unit.target: Annotation-egenskapen kan utvecklare ställa in <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Annotation>Egenskaper under den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanging>och <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanged>händelser för den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>kontroll.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanged> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanging> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Annotation>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Annotation"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Annotation"> </xref> objekt.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the new anchor location of the annotation.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger anteckningen nya fästpunkt plats.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Drawing.PointF"></xref> object that represents the new anchor position.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Drawing.PointF"> </xref> objekt som representerar den nya fästpunktens positionen.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the new annotation anchor point X location.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger den nya platsen för anteckningens ankare X-punkten.

trans-unit.source: When the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanging> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanging> events are raised, the NewAnchorLocationX property determines the new X coordinate of the annotation.
trans-unit.target: När den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanging>och <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanging>händelser aktiveras, egenskapen NewAnchorLocationX avgör den nya X-koordinaten för anteckningen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanging> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanging>

trans-unit.source: This information is useful when the annotation is newly anchored to a data point.
trans-unit.target: Den här informationen är användbar när anteckningen är förankrad nyligen på en datapunkt.

trans-unit.source: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_double" name="double" href=""></xref> value that represents the new annotation anchor point X location.
trans-unit.target: En <xref uid="langword_csharp_double" name="double" href=""> </xref> värde som representerar den nya platsen för anteckningens ankare X-punkten.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the new annotation anchor point Y location.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger den nya platsen för anteckningens ankare Y för platsen.

trans-unit.source: When the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanging> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanged> events are raised, the NewAnchorLocationY property determines the new Y coordinate of the annotation.
trans-unit.target: När den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanging>och <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanged>händelser aktiveras, egenskapen NewAnchorLocationY anger nya Y-koordinaten för anteckningen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanged> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanging>

trans-unit.source: This information is useful when the annotation is newly anchored to a data point.
trans-unit.target: Den här informationen är användbar när anteckningen är förankrad nyligen på en datapunkt.

trans-unit.source: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_double" name="double" href=""></xref> value representing the new annotation anchor point Y location.
trans-unit.target: En <xref uid="langword_csharp_double" name="double" href=""> </xref> -värde som representerar den nya anteckningens ankare datapunkts Y-platsen.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the new X coordinate location of the annotation.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger den nya X-koordinaten placeringen av anteckningen.

trans-unit.source: When the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanging> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanged> events are raised, the NewLocationX property defines the X-coordinate location of the annotation.

trans-unit.source: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_double" name="double" href=""></xref> value that represents the new X coordinate location of the annotation.
trans-unit.target: En <xref uid="langword_csharp_double" name="double" href=""> </xref> värde som representerar den nya X-koordinaten placeringen av anteckningen.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the new Y coordinate of the annotation location.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger nya Y-koordinaten för anteckningens plats.

trans-unit.source: When the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanging> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanged> events are raised, the NewLocationY property defines the Y-coordinate location of the annotation.
trans-unit.target: När den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanging>och <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanged>händelser aktiveras, egenskapen NewLocationY definierar Y-koordinaten placeringen av anteckningen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanged> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanging>

trans-unit.source: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_double" name="double" href=""></xref> value that represents the new Y coordinate of the annotation location.
trans-unit.target: En <xref uid="langword_csharp_double" name="double" href=""> </xref> värde som representerar nya Y-koordinaten för anteckningens plats.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the new location and size of the annotation.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger den nya platsen och storleken på anteckningen.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Drawing.RectangleF"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Drawing.RectangleF"></xref> object.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the new height of the annotation.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger den nya höjden av anteckningen.

trans-unit.source: When the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanging> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.AnnotationPositionChanged> events are raised, use the NewSizeHeight property to determine the new height of the annotation.

trans-unit.source: This information can be used when you resize the annotation.
trans-unit.target: Den här informationen kan användas när du ändrar storlek på anteckningen.

trans-unit.source: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_double" name="double" href=""></xref> value that represents the new height of the annotation.
trans-unit.target: En <xref uid="langword_csharp_double" name="double" href=""> </xref> värde som representerar den nya höjden av anteckningen.
